    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK460">
<l>nalliṉatti ṉūṅkut tuṇaiyillai tīyiṉatti </l>
<l>ṉallaṟ paṭuppatūu mil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is no greater help than the company of the good there is no greater source of sorrow than the company of the wicked.</l>
